tps://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ChatGPT-Image-May-3-2025-02_20_31-PM.png",title:"Green Gram",body:"Exporting the Finest Green Gram to Meet Global Demand"},{id:"10",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ChatGPT-Image-May-3-2025-02_27_35-PM.png",title:" Turmeric",body:"Turmerics vibrant hue and potential health benefits captivate with global markets."},{id:"11",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ChatGPT-Image-May-3-2025-02_27_37-PM.png",title:"Cumin",body:"The warm, distinctive flavor of cumin: A staple export from our fertile lands."},{id:"12",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/macro-shot-highlighting-cardamom-pod-details-free-photo.jpg",title:"Cardamom",body:"Discover the captivating aroma and flavor of our carefully selected cardamom."},{id:"13",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ChatGPT-Image-May-3-2025-02_20_28-PM.png",title:"Lentils",body:"Nutritious and versatile lentils, rich in protein and fiber for your meals."},{id:"14",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/coriander_main.jpg",title:"Coriander",body:"Experience the delicate, sweet flavor of our high-quality coriander seeds and powder."},{id:"15",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/istockphoto-1292299849-612x612-1.jpg",title:"Frozen food",body:"Premium frozen food made with the finest ingredients, flash-frozen for optimal freshness."},{id:"16",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/%E2%80%94Pngtree%E2%80%94fresh-testy-ripe-mango-fruit_15780770-scaled.jpg",title:" Mangoes",body:"Experience the rich, luscious flavor of our hand-picked mangoes."},{id:"17",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/glass-juice-is-being-poured-into-glass_1283804-746.jpg",title:"Mango pulps",body:"Rich and flavorful mango pulp, made from the finest ripe mangoes for a tropical treat."},{id:"18",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/mango-pickle.png",title:"Mango Pickle",body:"Experience the authentic, homemade taste of our traditional Indian mango pickle."},{id:"19",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bananajpg.png",title:"Banana",body:"Experience the smooth, satisfying sweetness of our ripe bananas."},{id:"20",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/istockphoto-1141245784-612x612-1.jpg",title:"Dried powder of banana",body:"Nutritious dried banana powder, ideal for smoothies, baking, and adding natural sweetness to recipes."},{id:"21",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/pomegranate.png",title:"Pomegranate",body:"Unlock the naturally sweet and slightly tart taste of these antioxidant-rich gems."},{id:"22",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/onion.png",title:"Onions",body:"Flavorful onions from our fields: The essential base for countless delicious dishes."},{id:"23",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/517UMQiXKOL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg",title:"Dry Onion Flaks",body:"Dehydrated onion flakes packed with bold flavor, perfect for seasoning and cooking."},{id:"24",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/red-onion-powder.jpeg",title:"Dry onion powder",body:"Finely ground dry onion powder, delivering robust flavor and convenience for all your culinary needs."},{id:"25",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pexels-victorino-2286776-scaled.jpg",title:"Potato",body:"Fresh, premium potatoes, ideal for versatile cooking and hearty meals."},{id:"26",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tomatoes.png",title:"Tomatoes",body:"Naturally sweet and tangy: The perfect tomatoes for your curries, dals, and more."},{id:"27",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Groundnut-e1746266712875.png",title:"Groundnuts",body:"Our quality groundnuts from Gujarat: Packed with flavor and wholesome goodness."},{id:"28",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Soybean.png",title:"Soybeans",body:"Experience the mild, subtly sweet flavor of our quality soybeans."},{id:"29",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/mustured_Seeds-e1746269252209.png",title:" Mustard Seeds",body:"Our flavorful mustard seeds: Adding a distinctive and zesty touch to your culinary creations."},{id:"30",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/sunflower-seeds-e1746269357895.png",title:"Sunflower Seeds",body:"Nutritious sunflower seeds: A crunchy and wholesome snack, packed with goodness."},{id:"31",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Tea.jpeg",title:"Tea",body:"Experience the refreshing and invigorating taste that awakens your senses."},{id:"32",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/roasted-coffee-beans-scaled.jpg",title:"Coffee Beans",body:"Fuel your day with the robust and invigorating taste of our premium coffee."},{id:"33",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/herbal_drinks.jpeg",title:"Herbal Drinks",body:"Find your moment of calm and revitalization with our thoughtfully crafted herbal infusions."},{id:"34",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/fruite_juice.jpeg",title:"Fruit Juices",body:"Quench your thirst with the vibrant and healthy goodness of our fruit juice."},{id:"35",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tomatoes_ketchup.jpeg",title:"Tomato Ketchup",body:"Tangy and sweet tomato ketchup: The perfect partner for your favorite snacks, made with ripe tomatoes."},{id:"36",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/196539-f0184.jpeg",title:"French Fries",body:"Enjoy the classic comfort of warm, delicious French Fries \u2013 a timeless favorite."},{id:"37",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Green-Peas.jpeg",title:"Green Peas",body:"Add a touch of vibrant color and wholesome nutrition with our fresh green peas."},{id:"38",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/mix-vegitables.jpeg",title:"Mixed Vegetables",body:"A vibrant medley of fresh vegetables from our local farms: Wholesome goodness in every bite."},{id:"39",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Broccoli-Cauliflower.jpeg",title:"Broccoli & Cauliflower",body:"Add a healthy and versatile duo to your cooking with our quality Broccoli & Cauliflower florets."},{id:"40",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/mix-barreies.jpg",title:" Frozen Berries",body:"Naturally sweet and bursting with flavor: Enjoy the year-round goodness of our frozen berries."},{id:"41",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/images-3.jpeg",title:"Honey ",body:"Pure natural honey, rich in flavor and packed with health benefits."},{id:"42",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/17417_17417_1620.jpg",title:"Isabgol",body:"natural psyllium husk for digestive health and regularity."},{id:"43",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Garlic.jpg",title:"Garlic",body:"Premium garlic, expertly processed for intense flavor and aroma in every dish."},{id:"44",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/orange-fruit-powder-isolated-white-background-with-clipping-path_762785-295839.jpg",title:"Dried powder of orange",body:"Zesty dried orange powder, perfect for adding citrus flavor to recipes."},{id:"45",img:"https://thewingsinternational.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/lemon-powder-citric-acid-powder-fresh-lemon-fruit-isolated-white-background_1235831-120036.jpg",title:"Dried powder of lemon",body:"Zesty dried lemon powder, perfect for adding a bright citrus flavor to your dishes and beve